'''[[Montenegrins (ethnic group)|Montenegrins]]''' form an ethnic minority in [[Republic of Macedonia|Macedonia]]. According to the 2002 Macedonian census  there are 2,003 ethnic Montenegrins in Macedonia.{{citation needed|date=September 2011}}

